summary: This is a joke MOD of \"The 1970 British science fiction television series UFO\".
descriptionHtml:
----------------
Joke MOD - UFO (ver 1.1)
----------------

This is a joke MOD of \"The 1970 British science fiction television series UFO\".

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16027

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17436


---
Author : hdela


---
This mod was built with Skyrim US Ver 1.5.24.0


---
Installation : Unzip the file, and overwrite Skyrim Data folder. Or drop the esp into your Skyrim Data directory.


---
Ver 1.1 :

The sound of UFO was added. This MOD can be overwritten. 


Ver 1.0 :

Single bed x2
No respawn container x4 (and no respawn dead human +1)
Disply case x1

Alchemy Workbench
Enchanting Workbench
Shrine of Kynareth


---
Enjoy!

by hdela
